o show some scatter which\nwe suggest is due to variations in pressure-induced molecular hydrogen opacity,\nwhich is sensitive to gravity and metallicity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2001 07:30:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
